    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay good to know. i was getting kind of worried. i also noticed i'm extra thirsty all the time and i've been peeing way more than usual too... i guess that's part of it working? i was thinking about maybe doubling my water intake just to stay ahead of it, is that a good idea?",
