      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? toxicity?? that sounds so scary. are you sure i can't just wait till morning to see if it passes? i'm kinda in the middle of something and i don't really have a way to get to the er right this second. if i just drink a ton of water and take some electrolytes, won't that help balance it out?",
